{"tid":681074,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"★[死神來了]蘋果零售店結業？52 名員工受影響！","createTime":"2018-05-27T17:09:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-28T05:48:14.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bb5b0157df43f156013e9c38a18a517068b76e71","tid":681074,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T17:09:46.000Z","msg":"蘋果公司近年不斷開設零售店，但面對目前科技產品普及下，用戶<span style=\"color: red;\">購買慾望減少，增長放緩</span>，似乎蘋果亦需要作出改變，近日有消息顯示，蘋果在美國地區，關閉一家零售店，影響 52 名員工。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，蘋果將關閉位於新澤西州大西洋城的一家零售店。蘋果向新澤西州提交了一份員工調整和再培訓通知，宣佈52人將因為這次結業店受到影響。蘋果在過去<span style=\"color: red;\">很少在不搬遷的情況下關閉一家零售店。</span><br />\n<br />\n蘋果表示，因為該區的旅遊人數大跌，不能再長期租下店舖，所以下了這個艱難的決定，將會為該店的員工，安排其他蘋果公司的工作崗位。<br />\n​<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/AppleRetailStore.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F03%2FAppleRetailStore.jpg&h=8c8c88c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2018/05/27/us-apple-retail-store-close/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2018%2F05%2F27%2Fus-apple-retail-store-close%2F&d=Zcr1ZrsZHQSr%2BmlG7wDQagHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=76cc117f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2018/05/27/us-apple-retail-store-close/</a>"},{"pid":"5f8dc2f88b0612b857b3fa856bd937a327d35a16","tid":681074,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T17:10:15.000Z","msg":"2018 drop to $0<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b95364596649acfee7ee99ab1ca88766ed73c146","tid":681074,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T21:04:33.000Z","msg":"香港生果store全線執笠，員工排隊食老綜，生果股價drop to 0 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acf2ccb88153ab4191cfeb5e1b45113896aaa45a","tid":681074,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T05:48:14.000Z","msg":"push"}]}